sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as OVMS REST (Drogon)<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as OVMS gRPC<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP/2
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler
    participant MPipe as MediaPipe Graph<br/>LLM Calculator
    participant CBatch as ContinuousBatching<br/>Pipeline
    participant MMgr as ModelManager
    participant MInst as ModelInstance
    participant OVRT as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant GenAI as OpenVINO GenAI
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure/HF<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 1: REST Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>KRBAC: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Kubernetes Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>REST: Forward (localhost)<br/>No encryption
    REST->>Handler: Route to KServe v2 handler
    Handler->>MMgr: getModelInstance(model, version)
    MMgr->>MInst: infer(request)
    MInst->>OVRT: compiledModel.infer()
    OVRT-->>MInst: InferenceResult
    MInst-->>MMgr: Response tensor
    MMgr-->>Handler: Prediction result
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>KRBAC: HTTP response
    KRBAC-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completions (Streaming SSE)
    Client->>REST: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API key (optional)<br/>stream: true
    REST->>Handler: Route to OpenAI v3 handler
    Handler->>Handler: isAuthorized() check
    Handler->>MPipe: Execute LLM graph
    MPipe->>CBatch: Schedule generation
    loop Continuous Batching - Token Generation
        CBatch->>GenAI: generateToken()
        GenAI-->>CBatch: Next token
        CBatch-->>MPipe: Token output
        MPipe-->>Handler: Partial result
        Handler-->>REST: SSE: data: {"choices":[...]}
        REST-->>Client: text/event-stream chunk
    end
    REST-->>Client: SSE: data: [DONE]

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 3: gRPC Inference (KServe ModelInfer)
    Client->>GRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>No auth (InsecureServerCredentials)
    GRPC->>MMgr: KFSInferenceServiceImpl.ModelInfer()
    MMgr->>MInst: infer(request)
    MInst->>OVRT: compiledModel.infer()
    OVRT-->>MInst: InferenceResult
    MInst-->>MMgr: Response tensor
    MMgr-->>GRPC: InferResponse proto
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    MMgr->>MMgr: Config poll (file_system_poll_wait_seconds)
    MMgr->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: Cloud provider credentials<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MMgr: Model files (IR XML + BIN / safetensors)
    MMgr->>OVRT: ov::Core::compile_model()
    OVRT-->>MMgr: Compiled model ready
    MMgr->>MMgr: Update model version map
